{"tid":496773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普重啟登月計劃　為往火星準備","createTime":"2017-12-12T04:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T08:40:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5560b15e8971bc38128ccb60c95fc8e873085fd7","tid":496773,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171212/s00005/d866594eeab75419945a649335a9c896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171212%2Fs00005%2Fd866594eeab75419945a649335a9c896.jpg&h=9281041f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周一（11日）簽署命令，指示美國太空總署（NASA），恢復載人航天探索計劃，讓美國太空人重返月球，為未來的火星之旅作準備。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮簽署「頭號太空政策指令」（Space Policy Directive 1）後表示，「這次我們不會只是插旗子和留下腳印」，新登月將包括長期探勘和利用。特朗普強調，「我們夢想遠大」，任務將為前往火星，以及未來前往更遠世界奠定基礎。<br />\n<br />\n這是繼1972年阿波羅17號（Apollo 17）執行登月任務後，美國再度計劃載人上月球。特朗普指，是次太空任務將重新聚焦於人類的探勘與發現上。<br />\n<br />\n白宮表示，特朗普6月已重建解散24年的國家太空委員會（National Space Council），聽取委員會建議後，決定改變美國的「載人航天政策」，讓美國從宇宙探索中獲得新知識，確保美國在未來的太空探索領域上領先全球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00005/1513050736287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00005%2F1513050736287&d=Yt7A02elDoz4Cy37BAznh7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=486005f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00005%2F1513050736287&h=24e80e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00005/1513050736287</a>"},{"pid":"40a79cb28e700ca6dd890401465585e66855906c","tid":496773,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"火星計劃唔係NASA一直做緊咩?<br />\n<br />\nORION  + SOLAR CITY + SPACE X"},{"pid":"d9ee94158cbe8fcec4ce52d8c68cf528382efa57","tid":496773,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"ci